00:13:17.770 --> 00:13:21.570
yes, we want to celebrate
but it is a call to action.

00:13:21.570 --> 00:13:23.990
It is a call to read your books.

00:13:23.990 --> 00:13:26.470
It is a call to publish
books of quality.

00:13:26.470 --> 00:13:29.290 position:56%
It is a call to write your own story

00:13:29.290 --> 00:13:32.270
and to critique the
stories that are out there.

00:13:32.270 --> 00:13:34.560
Engage with it.

00:13:34.560 --> 00:13:41.460
So yes, I'm excited that we get to
