00:13:41.460 --> 00:13:44.380
on in South Carolina, as
what's happened in Baltimore,

00:13:44.380 --> 00:13:48.580
what happened in Chicago with all
the places that are around us,

00:13:48.580 --> 00:13:52.520
all the violence, all
of the tragedies.

00:13:52.520 --> 00:13:57.410
One of the key things that we
get to do is know our stories

00:13:57.410 --> 00:14:01.890
and own our stories and
retell and share our stories.

00:14:01.890 --> 00:14:06.630
And I hope that this festival
