00:29:56.260 --> 00:29:58.980
than these beset the way.

00:29:58.980 --> 00:30:03.400
To sing the perfect song, and
by a half-note, lose the key.

00:30:03.400 --> 00:30:07.710
There the potent sorrow,
there the grief.

00:30:07.710 --> 00:30:11.200
The pale, sad staring
of life's tragedy.

00:30:11.200 --> 00:30:16.090
To have come near the perfect
