00:30:26.880 --> 00:30:33.080
This is indeed to be accursed for
if we mortals love, if we sing,

00:30:33.080 --> 00:30:36.050
we count our joys not
by what we have,

00:30:36.050 --> 00:30:39.300
but by what keeps us
from that perfect thing.

00:30:39.300 --> 00:30:45.290
Okay, now here's a poem I
