00:31:03.640 --> 00:31:05.390
Except the experience
for my life in DC.

00:31:05.390 --> 00:31:07.460
Please listen to me.

00:31:07.460 --> 00:31:08.780
They want me to fail.

00:31:08.780 --> 00:31:11.580
That's all they want me
to succumb to, failure.

00:31:11.580 --> 00:31:13.740
The prying eyes of the
ones who despise me try

00:31:13.740 --> 00:31:16.480
to make me feel like I have failed.

00:31:16.480 --> 00:31:18.690
What they do not know is
that I have prevailed.

00:31:18.690 --> 00:31:21.750
Prevailed over the prying
eyes for they look up to me.

00:31:21.750 --> 00:31:24.370
So I watch the sneaking
eyes trying to look

00:31:24.370 --> 00:31:27.410
at the mystical figure
that they despise.

00:31:27.410 --> 00:31:30.170
On the train, I smile and laugh.

00:31:30.170 --> 00:31:33.210
At work behind the bar, I smile

00:31:33.210 --> 00:31:36.250
and chuckle while keeping
up my belt buckle.

00:31:36.250 --> 00:31:40.150
Trying not to be that
black DC stereotype.

00:31:40.150 --> 00:31:44.750
Yes, that is all they see, the
tall violent untamed black animal

00:31:44.750 --> 00:31:49.310
with the dangerous
locks, the DC inhabitant.

00:31:49.310 --> 00:31:52.270
Hating on me because
I do what they can't.

00:31:52.270 --> 00:31:56.780
Now this is not only
for the people of white

00:31:56.780 --> 00:32:00.650
and red combined skin
before other complexions.

00:32:00.650 --> 00:32:04.750
This is about the war between
the light skins and dark.

00:32:04.750 --> 00:32:09.150
That's what they, those of the
higher power want us to say.

00:32:09.150 --> 00:32:12.380
Light versus dark, dark
chocolate versus not.

00:32:12.380 --> 00:32:16.230
What we are fighting each other
on the ground for attention,

00:32:16.230 --> 00:32:19.010
we are blinded by the
constant gun smoke.

00:32:19.010 --> 00:32:21.390
Our lungs are filled
-- our lungs are filled

00:32:21.390 --> 00:32:22.690
because of the weed smoke.

00:32:22.690 --> 00:32:26.000
Mother Earth's weed smoke
chokes us for pleasure.

00:32:26.000 --> 00:32:27.970
We get caught for the earth --

00:32:27.970 --> 00:32:30.190
we get caught for the earth
that we bought and breathed.

00:32:30.190 --> 00:32:34.230 position:56%
You best believe that our protectors
are now our fear dealing defectors.

00:32:34.230 --> 00:32:38.570
And now aren't -- yeah, I
myself tried to be friendly

00:32:38.570 --> 00:32:41.210
and give the killers a smile
so I can walk around with them

00:32:41.210 --> 00:32:43.600
for a while and not
minding their blank smiles,

00:32:43.600 --> 00:32:47.600 position:56%
hiding the hate but keeping control.

00:32:47.600 --> 00:32:50.420
I would rather not like them.

00:32:50.420 --> 00:32:56.020
I hang my head in fake like I have
respect in order to protect myself

00:32:56.020 --> 00:32:59.620
from lying on the floor silent
because of the bullet hole.

00:32:59.620 --> 00:33:02.580
They want that to be my future so
they could see another black one

00:33:02.580 --> 00:33:05.540
down and give no cares
and yes, it sucks.

00:33:05.540 --> 00:33:07.420
And so they realize
the best drink made

00:33:07.420 --> 00:33:10.760
for them isn't made
by me in Starbucks.

00:33:10.760 --> 00:33:15.830
It is I in public they do not
want to see but behind bar

00:33:15.830 --> 00:33:19.780
of a coffee shop or
eventually prison.

00:33:19.780 --> 00:33:22.520
But like I said, I have
risen above the contempt

00:33:22.520 --> 00:33:24.290
and kept my sanity in check.

00:33:24.290 --> 00:33:25.880
For I am that young black --

00:33:25.880 --> 00:33:31.510
