the triumphs and challenges

01:47:25.350 --> 01:47:26.650
of promoting literacy today.

01:47:26.650 --> 01:47:31.430
And so my beloved friends
and colleagues,

01:47:31.430 --> 01:47:35.370
the reading of literature has
always been very, very dear to me.

01:47:35.370 --> 01:47:39.190
I was also one of those people
who spend hours and hours

01:47:39.190 --> 01:47:46.510
in the library, and also recognized
that there were very few books

01:47:46.510 --> 01:47:49.440
