03:05:08.030 --> 03:05:14.010
When he saw nobody was looking,
he left that plantation,

03:05:14.010 --> 03:05:17.520
and for three generations
in the District of Columbia,

03:05:17.520 --> 03:05:21.370
if your name was Holmes, you
learned to read and write.

03:05:21.370 --> 03:05:25.560
You went to the public schools
of the District of Columbia

03:05:25.560 --> 03:05:27.040
and you learned to read and write

03:05:27.040 --> 03:05:28.680
because you remembered
Richard Holmes

03:05:28.680 --> 03:05:31.120
who did not know how
to read or write.

03:05:31.120 --> 03:05:32.950
But his son knew how
to read or write,

03:05:32.950 --> 03:05:39.640
and his son knew how
to read or write.

03:05:39.640 --> 03:05:43.360
So, when I understood
that here in our own --

03:05:43.360 --> 03:05:50.020
in the nation's Library of Congress
we were commemorating Juneteenth I

03:05:50.020 --> 03:05:54.780
