you find any people than the people

03:06:21.930 --> 03:06:26.400
of the District of Columbia
who are more grateful

03:06:26.400 --> 03:06:32.240
to what you're doing today as the
first to be liberated and who,

03:06:32.240 --> 03:06:36.610
